My VIM config 

##Installation

Grab the plugin submodules: cd ~/.vim && git submodule init && git submodule update

Make sure vim finds the vimrc file by  symlinking it: ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc


##HELPFUL SHORTCUT
%         goto corresponding bracket [,{,(
ci{       change within
ci(
ci"
t*        jump to *
dt*       delete to *
ct*       change to *
H         curser to top of screen
z+<enter> line to top of screen

--

GIT - recursive pull of submodules  
git submodule update --init

